					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Well, it looks like you've set a breakpoint for 37E.<br /><br />Now, reset the game, and play it till it writes to 37E. When it breaks, right click on the debugger in the gray blank area to the left of the disassembly, to the line just before the write to 37E. It should open the hex editor in view=ROM, to the exact location you want.<br /><br />That's what you edit. Then in the hex editor, save ROM as...new file.</div>

					
